## Non-goals for v2.35.4

- Semantic classifier (v2.35.5+, stub left in place)
- LLM classifier (v2.35.5+)
- Auto-promotion from augment to replace (manual operator decision)
- Runbook version history UI (future)

## Risk register

- Runbook body text quality matters. Seeded from existing prompt;
  evolve via UI editor over time.
- Keyword classifier is deliberately simple. Expected false-negatives
  on vague tasks. Fallback: no runbook injected, pre-v2.35.4 behaviour.
- `replace` mode may remove important context from the prompt. We
  explicitly defer enabling it until augment-mode trace diffs confirm
  the runbook body is self-sufficient.
- Runbook content is NOT sanitised for prompt injection attacks. Since
  only sith_lord can edit, this is acceptable for now. If role
  permissions expand, add content sanitisation.


